---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Disclaimer — Thee Rainers"
  description="Important disclaimers about the educational and physical training content on theerainers.com."
>
  <section class="bg-[#F7F5F2] px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">

      <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-black text-[#141414] text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-3">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-[#141414]/40 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: 26 May 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-legal">

        <h2>1. Educational content only</h2>
        <p>
          The content on theerainers.com — including the Blueprints, video library, free protocols, workshops, coaching programmes, and all written material — is provided for <strong>educational and fitness coaching purposes only</strong>. It is not intended to constitute, and does not constitute, medical advice, physiotherapy advice, mental health advice, or any other form of regulated professional advice.
        </p>
        <p>
          Nothing on this site should be interpreted as a diagnosis, treatment plan, or recommendation for any specific individual's health condition.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Physical risk and personal responsibility</h2>
        <p>
          Boxing, martial arts, and physical training of any kind involve inherent risks of injury, including serious injury or death. By accessing, purchasing, or using any content, programme, or coaching service from Thee Rainers, you acknowledge that:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>You participate voluntarily and assume full responsibility for your own safety.</li>
          <li>You should obtain clearance from a qualified medical professional before starting any new physical training programme, especially if you have any pre-existing injury, illness, or health condition.</li>
          <li>Thee Rainers, its founder, and its agents are not liable for any injury, illness, or loss arising from your participation in any training activity described or recommended on this site.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Consult a physician</h2>
        <p>
          Before beginning any exercise programme featured on this site, consult a licensed physician or sports medicine professional, particularly if you are over 40, have cardiovascular conditions, joint or musculoskeletal injuries, or any other condition that may be aggravated by vigorous physical activity.
        </p>

        <h2>4. No guarantee of results</h2>
        <p>
          Results from training programmes, coaching, and the use of any content on this site vary by individual and depend on factors including but not limited to: training consistency, physical condition, genetics, nutrition, sleep, and coaching environment. Any results described — whether in testimonials, marketing copy, or case studies — represent individual outcomes and do not guarantee that you will achieve the same results.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Testimonials</h2>
        <p>
          Any testimonials or statements about outcomes from past students or clients reflect their individual experience. They are not a guarantee of future results. Individual results will vary.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Third-party links</h2>
        <p>
          This site may contain links to third-party websites (including social media platforms, payment processors, and external resources). We have no control over the content, privacy practices, or accuracy of third-party sites, and we accept no responsibility for them. A link to a third-party site does not constitute an endorsement.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Affiliate relationships</h2>
        <p>
          <!-- TODO: Update this section if affiliate or referral arrangements are introduced. -->
          We do not currently participate in affiliate programmes or receive referral fees from third-party products or services featured on this site. If this changes, we will disclose it clearly at the point of recommendation.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Accuracy of information</h2>
        <p>
          We make every effort to ensure that the information on this site is accurate and up to date. However, we make no warranty that it is complete, current, or free of errors. We reserve the right to change or update information without notice.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this disclaimer: <a href="mailto:rainers@stepintoring.com">rainers@stepintoring.com</a>.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    color: #141414;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #141414;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .prose-legal p, .prose-legal li {
    color: #141414;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    padding-left: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #c84d3a;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .prose-legal a:hover {
    opacity: 0.75;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #141414;
  }
</style>
